            bindings = <
                &kp Q             &kp W           &kp E               &kp R           &kp T        &kp Y      &kp U            &kp I                &kp O            &kp P
                &hs LEFT_SHIFT A  &hm LEFT_ALT S  &hm LEFT_CONTROL D  &hm LEFT_GUI F  &kp G        &kp H      &hm RIGHT_GUI J  &hm RIGHT_CONTROL K  &hm RIGHT_ALT L  &hs RIGHT_SHIFT APOSTROPHE
&kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp Z             &kp X           &kp C               &kp V           &kp B        &kp N      &kp M            &kp COMMA            &kp DOT          &kp FSLH                    &kp FSLH
                                                  &kp DELETE          &lt 1 TAB       &kp SPACE    &kp ENTER  &lt 2 BACKSPACE  &lt 3 C_MUTE
